{"tid":1430131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"直接針對黑警搞一次大遊行","createTime":"2019-08-07T16:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T03:06:13.000Z","uid":111402,"like":35,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"47985097283f1ecafabfc559a7f1a452ae5563cd","tid":1430131,"uid":111402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:10:50.000Z","msg":"我睇到呢個po<br />\n<br />\n真心覺得應該搞多次百萬人大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1428398\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1428398</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n____________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n裡面提到 要再搞一次百萬和理非遊行<br />\n重申五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我個人認為不如呢次遊行先放低5大訴求<br />\n搞一次反黑警遊行<br />\n依家啲警犬已經失民心 普通街坊都對佢地咁不滿<br />\n咁樣個遊行隨時可以過2百萬<br />\n將佢地變用完嘅condom <br />\n以後嘅抗爭變得容易 或者 廢左警狗就直接逼到大陸出解放軍？<br />\n<br />\n正皮= 一定要提五大訴求<br />\n負皮= 搞一次反黑警和理非遊<br />\n<br />\nbetween<br />\n巴絲比啲意見 我上面啲分析岩唔岩<br />\n有錯大力屌"},{"pid":"914f522c2e685d40bf3bb4c0a4b5b24adf20d218","tid":1430131,"uid":111402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:11:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9dbc6596bfda35c71c5b35ab6f0361769dca732","tid":1430131,"uid":111402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:11:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5df718ecca6130085213a2868f026b34333b54a","tid":1430131,"uid":111402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:11:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a865634cf5e4c4eee84dfa4f05d0ba3f5f1e67ca","tid":1430131,"uid":111402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:12:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef677d6f6bff148c067d91f9a3c315fda6982368","tid":1430131,"uid":111402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:12:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14dddaf90bfd0a233fdfd99eee8b1af826c8073c","tid":1430131,"uid":111402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98f9a254eeaac01aa8769575f490f6f2f688e9f0","tid":143013